overview:
Prospectr Marketing is a premier lead generation and prospecting company with over 35 years of experience in B2B and B2C customer relationships.

We deliver quality prospects and developed leads to established and emerging businesses across diverse industries including manufacturing, media production, marketing, real estate, consumer services and information technology. We work closely with your team to implement “best practice” sales and marketing strategies to provide comprehensive solutions for lead nurturing, content development, market research, and campaign development & delivery using multimedia touch-points. Let Prospectr Marketing reach your target market efficiently and cost effectively. Visit www. www.prospectrmarketing.com
